# Loose club photos / hero images / flyers staged locally before being attached
# to Airtable. Drop them into working-photos/ to keep the repo root tidy.
# The extension rules below are a safety net so a stray image at root
# (e.g. dragged in from Downloads) doesn't get accidentally committed.
working-photos/
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png

# But keep the landing-page hero photo (referenced from styles.css)
!clubhouse-hero.png

